# DC SiteIQ — LLM configuration
#
# No environment variables are required to run this app.
# API keys are configured at runtime via the Settings (gear icon) in the sidebar.
# They are stored in the browser's localStorage and never sent to a backend.
#
# Supported providers:
#   - Google Gemini       → https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey
#   - OpenAI              → https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
#   - OpenRouter          → https://openrouter.ai/keys
#   - Any OpenAI-compatible provider (Groq, Mistral, Ollama, etc.)
